| `count` is 0       | Badge is not rendered.                       |
| `count` is negative| `validator` prevents invalid prop, defaults to 0. |
| `count` > 99       | Displays "99+" to keep badge compact.      |
| `count` is not a number | `validator` prevents invalid prop.       |

